{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation object to remove. This object must conform","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol","type":"text"}]}],"name":"annotation"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removing an annotation object dissociates it from the map view entirely,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing it from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method only when you want to hide or delete a given annotation."}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected."}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotation:","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"removeAnnotation:","modules":[{"nam